n the same change-detection cycle — but po-table's internal\nstate already has the row, so the visual state stays selected even though the data says\n`$selected: false`. This desync causes a second `(p-selected)` on the next click instead\nof `(p-unselected)`."],[2730,"**Root cause:** The correct Angular input alias is `p-maxlength` (no hyphen between `max` and `length`)."],[2771,"**Rule:** Every `po-table` generated in a `ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush` component MUST\nhave `[p-height]` set. No exceptions. A table inside an `@if` block is especially vulnerable."],[612,"**Seleção de template** — carrega `templates-test-base.md` + `templates-test-<família>.md`"],[808,"**Seletor:** `po-page-dynamic-detail`\\\n&#x2A;*Pacote:** `@po-ui/ng-templates`"],[788,"**Seletor:** `po-page-dynamic-edit`\\\n&#x2A;*Pacote:** `@po-ui/ng-templates`"],[756,"**Seletor:** `po-page-dynamic-search`\\\n&#x2A;*Pacote:** `@po-ui/ng-templates`"],[732,"**Seletor:** `po-page-dynamic-table`"],[380,"**Sem `any`**"],[3115,"**Sem arquivos de mock.** Nunca crie `*.mock.ts`, `*.data.ts` ou arquivos de mock separados.\nSe o app precisar de dados demo para desenvolvimento local (sem backend), adicione um `const DEMO_*: Model[] = [...]` no topo do arquivo do componente e carregue-o apenas no handler `error` de `carregar()`. Isso mantém o componente autocontido e limpo para produção."],[2854,"**Sempre** usar no submit — não omite campos desabilitados"],[2479,"**Setup em app.config.ts:**"],[378,"**Signals**"],[374,"**Standalone**"],[2704,"**Step 1 — Reduce the internal checkbox column via `::ng-deep`:**"],[2705,"**Step 2 — Calculate `p-width` values so that their sum + checkbox = panel width:**"],[2706,"**Step 3 — Use gap: 4px (not 8px) between panels** to maximize panel width:"],[3100,"**Substituições adicionais** além dos placeholders padrão:"],[2756,"**Symptom:** `po-table` renders correctly in the DOM but is invisible when the page is first\nnavigated to. It only becomes visible after the user moves th